The paper discusses a methodology and a prototype system for selecting data to use for training machine learning algorithms, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of crowdsourcing platforms for labeling data involves human computation (cs.HC), and the paper also discusses the management and generation of training datasets, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and database systems (cs.DB).
